{"type": "article", "id": 24131, "title": "这个日本漫画组合，要画《疯狂动物城》漫画版", "description": "Gurihiru 长期和漫威、迪士尼合作，画风萌萌哒。", "date": "2016-03-19T07:00:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22876, "name": "疯狂动物城"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 123, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110400pf34WmvK1qJeZFOC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">我们之前写<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/23404.html\">《疯狂动物城》同人漫画</a>的时候，介绍过一副作者 Gurihiru 的作品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110356ezUHx1ymZLNwkinF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41512605\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Gurihiru  3 月 17 日在 Twitter 上宣布，获得了迪士尼的授权，即将推出《疯狂动物城》的一个漫画版本。长度预计有 6 话。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110356R1F6k5Pp7SnLcGuA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.17735043\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110357NqhMCvsb7IOFkcKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3400335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110357Yaqkj0DgWI1p5yu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3400335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110358QXIyvqiHnKjkG7Bb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3400335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110358ZrJn7PNLW4dihOwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3400335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110359P9WQi6Z5HIuTCbzO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3400335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">原来 Gurihiru 是一个日本的漫画组合，由两个女生组成。她们现在为漫威等美国漫画公司工作，联合制作过《神奇四侠》、《雷神托尔和四勇士》（Thor and the Warriors Four），最新的作品是《降世神通》（Avatar: The Last Airbender）漫画版。\r\n\r\n《降世神通》\r\n\r\n同时也是美国尼克儿童频道 (Nickelodeon) 的动画。</p>\n<p class=\"\">她们也和迪士尼合作过，联合绘制过《勇敢传说》的漫画版《梅莉达》。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110359YOLCphe71b8v4Zoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110359jx0V7ygBq8OMp3Ie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.52905199\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">\r\n\r\nGurihiru \r\n\r\n的风格非常萌，和《疯狂动物城》的确很搭。期待她们的漫画。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这里是 \r\n\r\nGurihiru 的<a href=\"http://gurihiru.com/gallery.html\">官网</a>，<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gurihiru\">Twitter</a>。</p>\n\n"}